```
instance_name=mpack_instance_name, module_name=module_name,
zk_log_dir = ""
if zk_log_dirs:
  zk_log_dir = zk_log_dirs[0]
zk_pid_dirs = get_component_rundir_path...
```

Can we do this in the helper so that we don't have to pollute all of the Python code?
